n against Fabiano Caruana and won. Carlsen also used the opening again to draw with Caruana at the 2016 Chess Olympiad in Baku. Carlsen again used the opening as Black in a blitz game to defeat Viswanathan Anand at the 2019 Grand Chess Tour stop in Kolkata. So from time to time, it is employed at the elite level as an element of surprise. }
